data.title: Lou Reed’s Doctor Reveals Cause Of Death: “We Did Everything We Could”
data.meta_description: The cause of the death of Velvet Underground frontman Lou Reed, who passed away in his Long Island home yesterday, has been confirmed, with his doctor stating that the 71-year-old’s end-stage liver disease could no longer be treated.
